{"tid":2129603,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫管局一款由南京生產消毒噴霧敷料驗出洋蔥伯克氏菌 可引致肺部囊腫性纖維化","createTime":"2020-07-28T16:59:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T18:09:34.000Z","uid":14918,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a57a60cc0049bfbba513fc625259d7dd119d1bb9","tid":2129603,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:59:53.000Z","msg":"醫管局一款由南京生產消毒噴霧敷料驗出洋蔥伯克氏菌 <br />\n5腎病病人曾受感染<br />\n2020年07月28日22:02 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/07/facebook_20200728-CR-JUC1-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F07%2Ffacebook_20200728-CR-JUC1-1.jpg&h=d2a66443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據產品資料所示，JUC噴霧敷料是在皮膚或傷口表面產生物理膜，被界定為醫療儀器。<span class=\"red\">該產品由南京神奇科技開發有限公司製造</span>，並由JUC Biomaterial Co. Ltd供應。該供應商自願從市面回收有關批次的產品，並已設立電話熱線（2559 5227）解答相關查詢。而根據本地供應商的資料，受影響批次的產品曾供應予公立和私家醫院、私家診所及社區藥房。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/6856798-juc%E5%99%B4%E9%9C%A7%E9%A9%97%E5%87%BA%E6%B4%8B%E8%94%A5%E4%BC%AF%E5%85%8B%E6%B0%8F%E8%8F%8C-5%E5%90%8D%E8%85%8E%E7%97%85%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E6%9B%BE%E5%8F%97%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F6856798-juc%25E5%2599%25B4%25E9%259C%25A7%25E9%25A9%2597%25E5%2587%25BA%25E6%25B4%258B%25E8%2594%25A5%25E4%25BC%25AF%25E5%2585%258B%25E6%25B0%258F%25E8%258F%258C-5%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%2585%258E%25E7%2597%2585%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%2584%259F%25E6%259F%2593%2F&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=3814c1d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/6856798-juc%E5%99%B4%E9%9C%A7%E9%A9%97%E5%87%BA%E6%B4%8B%E8%94%A5%E4%BC%AF%E5%85%8B%E6%B0%8F%E8%8F%8C-5%E5%90%8D%E8%85%8E%E7%97%85%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA%E6%9B%BE%E5%8F%97%E6%84%9F%E6%9F